OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fstart for Thursday evening with
OL,7,Fincreasing amounts of cloud. Mist and
OL,8,Ffog most likely to affect eastern
OL,9,Fareas, with increasing chance of some
OL,10,Fshowers or rain overnight. This mainly
OL,11,Fin the northwest of the region.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FMost areas cloudy with chance
OL,14,Fof showers. Hazy sunshine at first
OL,15,Ftowards London and Kent. Some showery
OL,16,Frain arriving, probably turning
OL,17,Fheavier and more persistent in the
OL,18,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
