OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FConditions remaining cloudy and mild
OL,7,Fthrough the weekend and into Monday,
OL,8,Fwith widespread low cloud, some fog,
OL,9,Fand a chance of rain at times.
